      "body" : "Note the bitcoin codebase doesn't work in big endian at all right now. Also note that despite many headers/software making the assumption that endian is fixed at build time, that assumption is apparently not necessarily true in theory.\r\n\r\nThe cleanest option is to use a git submodule to embed LevelDB, at least until it's possible to build/link with system LevelDB.",
